Text: Your User Name and PasswordDear Subscriber Per your request here is your User Name and Password for The Wall Street Journal Online If you need further assistance please call online Journal Customer Service at or from amMidnight ET MondayFriday or you may email Subscribers calling from outside the United States can also find tollfree phone numbers by going to the following web page cspopuphtml Your User Name is brapp Your New Password is Note User Name and Password are casesensitive You may change your Password by following these directions First using your Web browser go to the following URL usercgibinsearchUserplactionpasswd Enter the User Name and Password shown above to login to the online Journal This page will allow you to choose a new Password Follow the instructions on the screen to choose a new Password You may also choose to Save your User Name and Password so you wont have to enter them again NOTE The Save your User Name and Password feature only works for the computer you are currently using After you have entered a new password you may go anywhere on the site Best Regards The Wall Street Journal Online Customer Service
